but isn't connected

44
00:01:43.505 --> 00:01:46.760
to some asset that
creates underlying value,

45
00:01:46.760 --> 00:01:49.085
there simply mediums of exchange.

46
00:01:49.085 --> 00:01:50.960
So the idea that the CAPM would

47
00:01:50.960 --> 00:01:52.610
have about really all currencies,

48
00:01:52.610 --> 00:01:54.980
