hold it in your portfolio,

49
00:01:54.980 --> 00:01:56.825
it's what we in economics call

50
00:01:56.825 --> 00:01:58.700
a zero net supply security.

51
00:01:58.700 --> 00:02:00.020
You really just should hold

52
00:02:00.020 --> 00:02:02.750
as little as possible
for transaction needs.

53
00:02:02.750 --> 00:02:05.360
