67
00:02:34.010 --> 00:02:35.645
currency pays no dividends.

68
00:02:35.645 --> 00:02:38.090
We're going to discuss this
further in lecture four.

69
00:02:38.090 --> 00:02:41.030
So thus the Gordon Growth Model
and the CAPM are

